features: Each set includes 15 pieces of hair accessories for your kids in school uniform colours. Choose from either the red, green or navy blue set.
Inside each 15 piece set are: Hairclips x2 shooting stars and x2 rainbows || Miniclips x2 hearts || Elastics x2 pom poms, x2 hearts, x2 rainclouds and x2 rainbows || Headband x1 aliceband

Plastic-free packaging includes x1 Classette canvas storage sack and x2 Classette brown paper elastic and clip cards. A lovely way to gift friends and also to store your Classette clips, elastics and headband.
Exuberant hair accessories, designed in London!
Crafted from high-quality leatherette, metallic, glitter and cotton blend fabrics. Each clip is wrapped with grosgrain grip ribbon to protect delicate hair.
